
GNU/Linux and Mac OSX
---------------------

$ wget http://download.camlcity.org/download/godi-rocketboost-20091222.tar.gz
$ tar zxvf godi-rocketboost-20091222
$ cd rocketboost-20091222
$ ./bootstrap --prefix /prefix/path
$ PATH=/prefix/path/bin:/prefix/path/sbin:$PATH
$ export PATH
$ ./bootstrap_stage2
$ godi_console perform -build godi-batteries

Cross-compilation
------------------
* No Godi required

Dependencies: 

$ batteries: https://github.com/ocaml-batteries-team/batteries-included.git
$ pcre: http://hg.ocaml.info/release/pcre-ocaml/archive/release-6.2.2.tar.gz
$ mingw32-ocaml (arch-AUR and debian [http://debian.glondu.net/mingw32/])

Ref: http://blog.rastageeks.org/ocaml/article/mingw32-ocaml-3-12-0
     http://blog.invokk.net/2011/04/cross-compilation-in-ocaml-using-mingw/
